ufetch

Tiny system info for Unix-like operating systems.

$ ufetch

     ________    user@host
    /  ______|   OS:        Slackware 15.0
    | |______    KERNEL:    Linux 5.15.27
    \______  \   UPTIME:    13 minutes
     ______| |   PACKAGES:  1591
  | |________/   SHELL:     bash
  |____________  DE:        XFCE

